text: Interstate 94 is an Interstate Highway in the United States. It goes from Billings, Montana east to Port Huron, Michigan at the Canada border. The route is long. It is the eighth longest Interstate Highway in the United States and the longest Interstate Highway that does not end in either a 0 or a 5. ==Auxiliary Routes Of I-94== *Interstate 294 *Interstate 394 *Interstate 494 *Interstate 694 *Interstate 794 *Interstate 894 ==References== 94
title: Interstate 94
